        "collapsible_tab_4YyHJK": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "HOW DOES THIS WORK?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "content": "<p>It sounds too good to be true right?  </p><p>Well, put simply, should anything ever happen to your Evertee, simply get in touch and we'll arrange a replacement garment.</p><p>That's it.<br/></p><p>Oh, and unlimited replacements.</p><p>How are we so confident?</p><p>Our premium heavyweight t-shirt is carefully and ethically crafted from 100% combed cotton.</p><p>Designed for unmatched durability, timeless comfort, and sustainability, it’s built to handle whatever life throws at it. </p><p>Featuring a classic fit, double-needle stitching, and pre-shrunk fabric, Evertee is as tough as it is soft.</p><p>Save money, save the planet, make Evertee the only t-shirt you’ll ever need.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_rr63KB": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "ABOUT THE TEE",
            "icon": "shirt",
            "content": "<ul><li>Premium fitted crew neck tee</li><li>Thick 210g weight</li><li>Longer body length</li><li>100% combed ringspun cotton</li><li>Soft tag printed for extra comfort</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_JXrb7D": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "DELIVERY & RETURNS",
            "icon": "box",
            "content": "<p>Orders placed by 2pm are shipped same day. If this falls on a weekend, it will be shipped the next working day. <br/><br/>Allow 1-3 working days for UK delivery.</p><p>Allow 7-8 working days for USA / ROW delivery</p><p>We offer a no quibble 28 day return policy. We just ask that the tee is in the same condition as we sent it.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_3Brz6X": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "EVERT(R)EE",
            "icon": "leaf",
            "content": "<p>Not only does making the switch to Evertee help save over 100 trees, but we'll plant an extra one for each Evertee sold, just for good measure!</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_B4eDpp": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "SIZING",
            "icon": "ruler",
            "content": "<p>Our premium heavyweight t-shirt is carefully and ethically crafted from 100% combed cotton. </p><p>Fitting is true to size, but if it's not the right size, we offer a free no quibble 28 day return / exchange window.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
